{"tid":1668881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於「v煞」面具聚籌","createTime":"2019-10-22T08:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T13:26:55.000Z","uid":310903,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"47c45518841b3f7b6840aa174b5107258fcc4b03","tid":1668881,"uid":310903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/萬人「v煞」蒙面抗極權/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8Cv%E7%85%9E%E3%80%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%8A%97%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%2F&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=a6e572e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/萬人「v煞」蒙面抗極權/</a><br />\n<br />\n話說係TG group 見到呢個聚籌，就㩒入去睇下<br />\n<br />\n點知一睇d面具係喺淘寶訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1e4czUM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1e4czUM.png&h=b8094b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92chL1u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92chL1u.png&h=a6213a98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVSYvtb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVSYvtb.png&h=d2457fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白團隊都係想遊行時一齊戴 v 煞 面具更加有noise 亦都知道你地之前買面具 派面具 係花左唔少人力 物力 心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果要上淘寶訂 會唔會同我地既本意背道而馳呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實自己畫/自己整會唔會更好呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WNlKyUNxAHi85JN7abocl-g5a4QI-Nha/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1WNlKyUNxAHi85JN7abocl-g5a4QI-Nha%2Fview&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=344d413b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WNlKyUNxAHi85JN7abocl-g5a4QI-Nha/view</a><br />\n<br />\n附上自製 v煞 面具link"},{"pid":"76d27afedfc5371c5f287b80d977710daef133b7","tid":1668881,"uid":314136,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"比完錢 然後比公安扣起 喊都無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403ce0d4a74697cb9cb3805f9c03f6070fc01ee1","tid":1668881,"uid":310903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:52:50.000Z","msg":"P 牌 推唔郁 求幫<br />\n唔希望見到廿幾萬就咁攞左去淘寶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知廿幾萬幫到幾多小朋友開飯"},{"pid":"97a474674e96415a8f04b9e0a4ba6fc544d972ba","tid":1668881,"uid":310903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"76d27afedfc5371c5f287b80d977710daef133b7","tid":1668881,"uid":314136,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"比完錢 然後比公安扣起 喊都無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n買咁多面具寄香港 好難唔懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9617526d9964866779f34af451e078229d758156","tid":1668881,"uid":12597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"Amazon會唔會有<br />\n呢啲嘢淘寶高風險呀"},{"pid":"d6ed7ae7b285ad5ac08135ab1db29077a51e299d","tid":1668881,"uid":310903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9617526d9964866779f34af451e078229d758156","tid":1668881,"uid":12597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"Amazon會唔會有<br />\n呢啲嘢淘寶高風險呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"有呀 5-10美金一副 但唔確定產地<br />\nv煞團隊不如上amazon 同賣家了解下產地, 大量購入有無得平<br />\n幫我地搞代購啦"},{"pid":"0d468bc8cc2ccfa542228